    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>rested steak</strong> with the<strong> parmentier potatoes</strong>, <strong>roasted mushroom</strong>, <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> and <strong>salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Spoon the <strong>bistro butter</strong> over the steak</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
